@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_narmml(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.33) * (v2 + 0.63 * v1 + 0.53)) + wp.cos(tmp))
    v2 = (0.26 - (v1 - (v1 + 0.37 + v1 + 0.90)))
    v2 = (0.34 - ((v1 + 0.95 - tmp + 0.24) / (v1 + 0.98 + tmp + 0.75)))
    v2 = 0.39
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (v1 / tmp)
    tmp = wp.sin((v0 * (tmp + 0.01 - v2 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
